title: Trainwreck reunion! Amy Schumer has a bit of trouble remembering co-star Vanessa Bayer in these SNL promos
text: 0 US TV News Trainwreck reunion! Amy Schumer has a bit of trouble remembering co-star Vanessa Bayer in these SNL promos Friday, Oct 9 2015, 01:12   Twitter Share on Google+ Amy Schumer is riding high off the success of Trainwreck and a recent Emmy win – and it looks like all this fame is going to her head.The comedian reunites with Trainwreck co-star Vanessa Bayer for new Saturday Night Live promos, and has a bit of trouble remembering her on-screen sister.Schumer might want to heed Bayer's dire warning – this weekend could be where it "all comes crashing down" if she's not careful.Joining Amy Schumer on SNL will be musical guest The Weeknd for both stars' first-ever appearances on the sketch show. Saturday Night Live airs at 11.30pm ET on NBC.
